> Continue button and even that was named verify.html which to the unwary
> is a benign name.  However as Thunderbird had already flagged it as spam
> when I clicked the button (all fields empty of course) I got a warning
> and an IP address which it turns out is in America.
> 
> That could easily catch the unwary especially if their mail client had
> not already pinged it as a scam.
